<span class="line"><span style="--shiki-light:#E45649;--shiki-dark:#E06C75;">Sec-Fetch-Mode</span><span style="--shiki-light:#A626A4;--shiki-dark:#C678DD;">:</span><span style="--shiki-light:#50A14F;--shiki-dark:#98C379;"> navigate</span></span>
